{"tid":1717871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭立：如果你堅持抗爭者是無罪, 你應該否定香港特區政府的合法性","createTime":"2019-11-13T17:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T17:08:12.000Z","uid":70301,"like":100,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b327cb9d33519980e77cdf4568bad14d9f05e1df","tid":1717871,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:00:39.000Z","msg":"先把結論放在前頭, 如果你堅持抗爭者是無罪, 你應該否定香港特區政府的合法性. 由 1997 年至今運作了 22 年的特區政府, 可能會再存在更久時間, 是一個非法政權. <br />\n<br />\n雖然這對很多人來說是難以想像, 甚至大家一輩子都是活在這政權下. 但是如果你要堅持, 所有的抗爭者皆是無罪的話, 我們就要不承認公安條例, 也就是說, 我們要否認 1997 年臨時立法會的立法權力. <br />\n<br />\n而香港在 1997 年之後, 是一個被入侵者非法佔據狀態, 如果這個佔據狀態結束, 則一切在這段期間的法律與行政, 都會預設無效. 因此, 公安條例不會有效, 所以根據公安條例所做的檢控, 皆不成立. <br />\n<br />\n而抗爭者所做的一切行為, 都是抵抗侵略的行為. 因此是合法的, 因為一切的出發點都在於維護香港的合法權力, 那是淪陷時期的反抗活動, 而所有對於這些反抗活動的鎮壓, 都是非法行為. <br />\n<br />\n任何一個香港人, 為了協助佔領者維持統治權力, 而對於香港人施行暴力, 本身應該是犯罪行為. <br />\n<br />\n這些當然不會現在就實現, 就像在 1943 年的香港, 你違反皇軍的法律就是犯法, 皇軍就有權合法地抓你和判你刑. 但是光皇軍的政權完結, 皇軍所作的一切審判與行為, 則全部都不再合法, 而我們不會說, 在 1943 年有人傷害了皇軍, 就基於法律面前人人平等, 皇軍都有老豆老母生也是依法(他們的法)行事就告傷人. <br />\n<br />\n在這樣的框架下, 抗爭者的一切行為皆是自衛以及愛國抗爭的一部份, 不僅不是犯罪, 更是需要留在史冊的英雄行為. <br />\n<br />\n所以我們對於抗爭者所做的一切行為, 也只能以這個態度視之, 雖然我們不清楚非法政權和佔據期, 何時才會結束, 可能是五年, 可能是十年, 可能是三十年. 但我們如果堅持抗爭者無罪, 則我們就應該要堅持該法律本身是非法的. 如果我們承認公安條例, 以及立公安條例的立法權力, 那麼我們就等於接受抗爭者是有罪的.<br />\n<br />\n當然如果你採用了上述的主張, 你明顯不效忠基本法, 選舉這件事就跟你無緣了."},{"pid":"bab0bab861f7d1285705cb2117453a79f0d3b0b5","tid":1717871,"uid":215784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:01:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c6b265570169bc00b7fca29c51af8e79b1adee2","tid":1717871,"uid":70301,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！！！<br />\nHong Kong Independence！！！<br />\n<br />\n即管屌我係五毛屌我係鬼，還掂你哋都屌我唔少<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981a9978356187a4ffdba66349ba04f4e6d4ab35","tid":1717871,"uid":35211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:03:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d791876213b2ca1d04b5236239c4eeb6b5118711","tid":1717871,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:03:46.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"00d31f835fe244e316bda22cfaa5f296baf5a1e2","tid":1717871,"uid":70301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"in 鄭立，we trust <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48793ca0e708f153cca302600aeb5e2991bc585","tid":1717871,"uid":70301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:04:52.000Z","msg":"香港人全面反枱，反佢老味，同共匪死過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"265689671a0171561563cf954d286f366fce895a","tid":1717871,"uid":272821,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VFKRR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VFKRR.jpg&h=90de4d05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46b9fe3efc0a0ca5bb4833f3eeac7f2d4a50a6da","tid":1717871,"uid":266503,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:06:56.000Z","msg":"我非常懷疑政府合法性 <br />\n<br />\n講非法治國家都叫俾面"},{"pid":"0d145e3f2032002fd98ce268879ae929e19c4f34","tid":1717871,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"265689671a0171561563cf954d286f366fce895a","tid":1717871,"uid":272821,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VFKRR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VFKRR.jpg&h=90de4d05&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:08:27.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！！！<br />\nHong Kong Independence !!!"},{"pid":"dc66c14d2ecaa756bab0fc5b3b5d3d51c99583c7","tid":1717871,"uid":243854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:08:32.000Z","msg":"一早講過政權違法，但點樣推翻先難"},{"pid":"7a4b50b41518420400b8ea7fba1c61d5b5386366","tid":1717871,"uid":254594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"所以中英聯合聲明失效是關鍵<br />\n既成事實 但英國唔確認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ebd65222411052bc66fe1a7fc4d9556fc82e57","tid":1717871,"uid":53524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"首先你要否定基本法既正當性"},{"pid":"57cee3c3c9a90c7de07e21422421fc7dc6ba53ce","tid":1717871,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eea35b2cca6409386fd4bb128a25962d0fad8d7","tid":1717871,"uid":262674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:22:00.000Z","msg":"好正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁要問<br />\n點樣可以否定佢既合法性<br />\n公開宣稱？<br />\n國際宣稱？<br />\n打番黎？<br />\n<br />\n要公開宣布中共係非法統治？<br />\n依家係咪真係可以咁行？<br />\n定係遲啲可以或者唔可以？"},{"pid":"472d0c987884ae7df7a986b891eb8b186968fafb","tid":1717871,"uid":262674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"53ebd65222411052bc66fe1a7fc4d9556fc82e57","tid":1717871,"uid":53524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:11:13.000Z","msg":"首先你要否定基本法既正當性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:22:32.000Z","msg":"或者英國交還畀中國係唔合法"},{"pid":"c82f5dc40ec6b6377bfe8ed01ef187743713d9d2","tid":1717871,"uid":70301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4eea35b2cca6409386fd4bb128a25962d0fad8d7","tid":1717871,"uid":262674,"like"